{"tid":497710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 有粒石頭瘡係塊臉又冇膿頭 成個星期啦 點搞！","createTime":"2017-12-13T05:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T04:44:34.000Z","uid":139826,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"731dd12aa6f531342bdb7b54cbe8425bdb6410a5","tid":497710,"uid":139826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:14:23.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲可以分享下經驗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有好大粒係下巴 又黑又腫咁<br />\n諗住等佢出咗膿頭可以擠啦<br />\n點撚知成個星期都冇 得一舊嘢腫咗係到<br />\n好醜怪 唔想見到人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試過茶a酸 又試過用娥羅納英焗佢 都唔work<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cc8abf19fe4f7c16610d6b0ab8a1606143e4e5","tid":497710,"uid":15758,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:16:10.000Z","msg":"唔好擠 之前擠到啲油爆哂勁爽 但個印跟左我兩三年"},{"pid":"8b7657ba4a6be3a4c76085143e1da97cd48e42e9","tid":497710,"uid":39825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"食返餐m記谷佢出黎<br />\n利申試過"},{"pid":"c77194e84214c5a9c30a672e0c0b46565e37950e","tid":497710,"uid":56999,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:22:00.000Z","msg":"如果擠  記住拍片"},{"pid":"5c2096738086df485bed6b84ab4084da47f82b6f","tid":497710,"uid":139826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好擠 之前擠到啲油爆哂勁爽 但個印跟左我兩三年</blockquote><br />\n我諗住有膿頭之後等佢爆 再用痘痘貼<br />\n但頭都冇我真係唔知可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416bde339af584767ea6586a04a3a8daf6f88593","tid":497710,"uid":139826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:28:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食返餐m記谷佢出黎<br />\n利申試過</blockquote><br />\n我前晚食過雞煲火鍋 粒嘢谷到好行<br />\n第二朝又冇事 照舊黑腫痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7438a911ce6c3192db02ca662ae8ef6d68e095","tid":497710,"uid":142314,"like":